Eldest Young Master,

27
00:01:33,060 --> 00:01:36,660
I did agree to marry you,

28
00:01:36,980 --> 00:01:38,540
but before you tell Madam,

29
00:01:38,540 --> 00:01:41,300
shouldn't you have discussed it
with me first?

30
00:01:42,660 --> 00:01:45,780
I admit I wanted to marry you
as soon as possible.

31
00:01:46,620 --> 00:01:48,220
I thought you felt the same way.

32
00:01:50,860 --> 00:01:51,380
I...

33
