such a weight on my heart?

39
00:02:28,820 --> 00:02:29,660
After the wedding,

40
00:02:30,020 --> 00:02:31,600
I'll gain access
to the Pei family's most closely guarded

41
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:32,380
fragrance-making techniques,

42
00:02:32,860 --> 00:02:34,540
and I'll be one step closer
to uncovering the truth

43
00:02:34,540 --> 00:02:35,540
behind my aunt's abduction.

44
00:02:43,580 --> 00:02:44,180
Let's go.

45
00:02:57,980 --> 00:02:58,940
Sirs,

46
00:02:59,420 --> 00:03:00,940
you brought me here

47
00:03:01,140 --> 00:03:02,420
and yet haven't killed me.

48
00:03:02,660 --> 00:03:04,620
That means
I must still be of some use to you.

49
00:03:05,700 --> 00:03:07,860
How about this? I'll pay you.

50
00:03:07,860 --> 00:03:09,860
Whoever hired you to abduct me,
how much did they offer?

51
00:03:10,100 --> 00:03:11,300
I'll pay double.

52
00:03:12,940 --> 00:03:14,260
Triple if you like.

53
00:03:15,540 --> 00:03:17,020
I can also write to the Pei family.

54
00:03:17,060 --> 00:03:18,420
Someone from the Pei family
will come to rescue me.

55
00:03:19,860 --> 00:03:22,180
No wonder you've caught the attention
of the two Pei brothers,

56
00:03:22,420 --> 00:03:24,100
you are quite a beauty indeed.

57
00:03:25,420 --> 00:03:26,060
Sir.

58
00:03:27,380 --> 00:03:27,900
You...

59
00:03:28,260 --> 00:03:29,940
Do you know who my master is?

60
00:03:30,420 --> 00:03:32,940
My master is Pei Jinghang.

61
00:03:33,620 --> 00:03:34,900
With his terrible temper,

62
00:03:35,260 --> 00:03:36,500
if he were to get angry,

63
00:03:36,500 --> 00:03:38,780
I… I'm afraid
you wouldn't be able to handle it.

64
00:03:39,340 --> 00:03:40,140
Is that a threat?

65
00:03:40,980 --> 00:03:42,420
Once you're taken to the Quluo Kingdom,

66
00:03:42,500 --> 00:03:44,180
you'll sell for no less
than a thousand gold.

67
00:03:44,180 --> 00:03:45,820
Pei Jingheng is nothing.

68
00:03:45,820 --> 00:03:47,100
What are you doing?

69
00:03:48,940 --> 00:03:50,820
Hold on. Lustful as you may be,

70
00:03:51,100 --> 00:03:52,100
don't ruin her worth.

71
00:03:52,460 --> 00:03:53,420
Once this job is done,

72
00:03:53,620 --> 00:03:55,260
we'll have enough
to settle down in Quluo.

73
00:03:55,860 --> 00:03:57,460
I became a kidnapper because I was sick

74
00:03:57,460 --> 00:03:58,300
of being pushed around by women.

75
00:03:59,100 --> 00:04:00,860
Why is it always men who are humiliated?

76
00:04:02,420 --> 00:04:06,060
Today, I'll do as I please with her.

77
00:04:06,140 --> 00:04:07,260
Help!

78
00:04:14,420 --> 00:04:15,060
Zhiyao.

79
00:04:24,820 --> 00:04:26,940
I knew you'd come to save me.

80
00:04:29,100 --> 00:04:29,780
It's all right now.

81
00:04:33,820 --> 00:04:34,620
Let's go.

82
00:04:38,660 --> 00:04:40,300
I just sprained my ankle.

83
00:04:41,140 --> 00:04:41,820
Villains!

84
00:04:42,740 --> 00:04:43,820
Release Zhiyao at once!

85
00:04:44,620 --> 00:04:45,980
How dare you ruin my plans!

86
00:04:46,220 --> 00:04:47,020
I'll kill you!

87
00:05:14,020 --> 00:05:15,060
Are you all right, Jinglan?

88
00:05:17,420 --> 00:05:18,980
Eldest Young Master,
what happened to you?

89
00:05:19,820 --> 00:05:20,620
I'm fine.

90
00:05:20,980 --> 00:05:21,900
That's good.

91
00:05:23,140 --> 00:05:23,860
Eldest Young Master.

92
00:05:25,300 --> 00:05:26,180
