Eldest Young Master, don't worry.

101
00:05:51,740 --> 00:05:53,900
Rest in bed for another month or so,

102
00:05:54,020 --> 00:05:54,940
and you'll be fully recovered.

103
00:05:55,500 --> 00:05:57,740
But in just a few days,
it will be my wedding day.

104
00:05:58,140 --> 00:05:59,420
Is there any way

105
00:05:59,900 --> 00:06:01,060
to help the wound heal faster?

106
00:06:04,500 --> 00:06:06,140
It takes time
for muscles and bones to heal.

107
00:06:06,340 --> 00:06:08,060
If you get out of bed too soon,

108
00:06:08,260 --> 00:06:09,980
it will only make the injury worse.

109
00:06:16,180 --> 00:06:17,180
Thank you, sir.

110
00:06:17,660 --> 00:06:18,500
It's my job.

111
00:06:31,140 --> 00:06:33,500
Eldest Young Master, you were injured
all because of Miss Song.

112
00:06:34,180 --> 00:06:35,820
She came to visit you
in the first couple of days,

113
00:06:36,340 --> 00:06:37,740
