to stop her.

115
00:06:40,460 --> 00:06:41,500
Surely he did it on purpose.

116
00:06:42,340 --> 00:06:42,980
Enough!

117
00:06:46,540 --> 00:06:48,420
Zhiyao can only be my wife.

118
00:07:04,300 --> 00:07:05,700
I've come this far.

119
00:07:06,940 --> 00:07:08,260
There's no turning back.

120
00:07:15,500 --> 00:07:16,260
Father,

121
00:07:17,300 --> 00:07:17,940
Mother,

122
00:07:18,660 --> 00:07:19,780
