123
00:07:21,460 --> 00:07:23,460
I will find my aunt as soon as possible.

124
00:07:36,220 --> 00:07:38,500
First, bow to Heaven and Earth.

125
00:07:47,940 --> 00:07:50,140
Second, bow to the parents.

126
00:07:56,820 --> 00:07:57,620
All right.

127
00:07:59,940 --> 00:08:02,020
Bow to each other.

128
00:08:15,300 --> 00:08:16,020
My Lady.

129
00:08:25,540 --> 00:08:26,700
How come it's you?

130
00:08:35,020 --> 00:08:36,300
If you change your mind now,

131
00:08:37,100 --> 00:08:38,260
I'll take you out of here.

132
00:08:38,740 --> 00:08:39,840
The ceremony is complete,

133
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:42,220
